race.description: Greetings From Krc - Tis The Season Maiden Plate
race.comment: DARE TO LOVE (8) steps out to 1200m again today following a rather disappointing performance at Ballina last time out. She's been run off her feet her past couple and now out to this trip looks to suit much better. Still looking for her maiden win but she finds a suitable race today. SHE'S GOT IT (9) was in good touch here two back before going to the Sunshine Coast last start and finishing well back. Back to this track and trip today is a good move and she appears the likely leader from the draw. Will take catching. KENNY THE BAKER (13) trialled well coming into this campaign but disappointed first-up when a $6 chance on the Sunshine Coast. The wide draw is a niggle, but getting out to 1200m can see him improve. Not willing to discount. BATTLE WORTHY (18) can be in the finish first-up.
